  "texts": [
    "To indicate model effectiveness, we also conduct uncertainty analysis.",
    "We employ the Monte Carlo dropout (MCD) method for uncertainty quantification in this research.",
    "Specifically, we employ the MCD method to measure epistemic uncertainty, which is usually caused by the lack of training data.",
    "In other words, with more training data, such model uncertainty can be reduced.",
    "Before introducing MCD, we briefly discuss the traditional dropout method, which is only applied in the training stage by switching off some randomly selected neurons."
